    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    AdminController
    The AdminController class is responsible for managing the admin interface in the PhotosFX application.
    Album
    The Album class represents a photo album that contains a collection of photos.
    AlbumController
    The AlbumController class is responsible for managing the album interface in the PhotosFX application.
    Data
    The Data class holds static fields and metohds used by the whole program.
    DisplayController
    The DisplayController class is responsible for managing the display of a photo in the PhotosFX application.
    ExitOptionsController
    The ExitOptionsController class is responsible for managing the exit options in the PhotosFX application.
    LoginController
    The LoginController class is responsible for managing the login interface in the PhotosFX application.
    Photo
    The Photo class represents a photo that contains a collection of tags.
    PhotoOptionsController
    The PhotoOptionsController class is responsible for managing the options available for a selected photo in the PhotosFX application.
    Photos
    The @code Photos class is the main entry point of the application.
    SearchController
    The SearchController class is responsible for managing the search functionality in the PhotosFX application.
    SlideshowController
    The SlideshowController class is responsible for managing the slideshow functionality in the PhotosFX application.
    Tag
    The Tag class represents a tag that is part of a Photo.
    User
    The User class represents a user that contains a collection of albums.
    UserController
    The UserController class is responsible for managing the user interface in the PhotosFX application.
